zh_CN.DialogText: 这才对嘛，末日里我们就应该互相帮助

en_US.DialogText: That's right. We should help each other at the end of the day

zh_CN.DialogText: 你最好赶紧给我滚出这里。

en_US.DialogText: You'd better get out of here,idiot。

zh_CN.DialogText: 他把吃的装进公文包里，顶着啤酒肚离开了

en_US.DialogText: He packed his food into his beer belly and left

zh_CN.DialogText: 真倒霉，就当是花钱消灾了

en_US.DialogText: It's bad luck. It's like spending money to eliminate the disaster

zh_CN.DialogText: 至少不会在公社里被传闲话了
自我安慰一番，今天的末日生活还要继续

en_US.DialogText: Comfort yourself. Today's Doomsday life will continue

zh_CN.DialogText: 真希望在这些困难日子里，这种人不要再出现了

en_US.DialogText: I really hope this kind of person will not appear again in these difficult days

zh_CN.DialogText: 公社里这种人究竟还有多少啊？

en_US.DialogText: How many such people are there in the commune?
